org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.multiobjective.wasfga

Class WASFGA<S extends Solution<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.impl.AbstractEvolutionaryAlgorithm<S,Result>
      • org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.impl.AbstractGeneticAlgorithm<S,List<S>>
        • org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.multiobjective.mombi.AbstractMOMBI<S>
          • org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.multiobjective.wasfga.WASFGA<S>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Runnable, Algorithm<List<S>>, DescribedEntity
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GWASFGA, WASFGAMeasures

    public class WASFGA<S extends Solution<?>>
extends AbstractMOMBI<S>
    Implementation of the preference based algorithm named WASF-GA on jMetal5.0
    Author:
    Juanjo Durillo This algorithm is described in the paper: A.B. Ruiz, R. Saborido, M. Luque "A Preference-based Evolutionary Algorithm for Multiobjective Optimization: The Weighting Achievement Scalarizing Function Genetic Algorithm". Journal of Global Optimization. May 2015, Volume 62, Issue 1, pp 101-129 DOI = {10.1007/s10898-014-0214-y}
    See Also:
